  <p class="text text-center">There are a ton of categories to compete in! View on Devpost for the complete list.</p>
  <p class="text text-center">
    Several companies are sponsoring their own category as well.
    <br/>
    If you're interested, stop by their table!
  </p>
  <p class="text text-center">
    <strong>Please submit your final project to Devpost</strong>
    by the submission deadline on Sunday morning. Judging will take place Sunday afternoon, and all teams must be present to be considered.
  </p>
  <p class="text text-center">
    You will
    <strong>not</strong>
    be judged based on your Devpost submission profile. However, you must select the appropriate categories you are competing in.
  </p>
  <br/>
  <div class="text-center">
    <%= btn_link_to 'Open Devpost &raquo;'.html_safe, 'https://brickhackv.devpost.com' %>
  </div>
</div>
